<body>
<div class="container-fluid">
    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-md-6 left-column"></div>
        <div class="col-md-6 right-column">
                <br />
                <br />
                
            <div class="welcome-box">
                <h1>歡迎回來！</h1>
                <p>智慧養殖，從掌蛋記錄開始</p>
                <p>
                  
                        <a id="login-link" href="#">已有帳號？立即登入</a>
                    </p>
            </div>
            <br />
            <div class="login-box">
                <h1>註冊</h1>
